constructor.details: We enforce implementations of this contract to be disabled as a security measure to prevent delegate      calls to the SELFDESTRUCT opcode, irrecoverably disabling all the proxies using that implementation.

params.votesAbstain: The number of abstaining votes for the proposal.
params.votesAgainst: The number of votes against the proposal.
params.votesFor: The number of votes for the proposal.

executeQueuedProposal(bytes).details: Due to possible reentrancy, one cannot rely on the invariant that proposal payloads are executed atomically.      As follows: If Proposal A is composed of MetaTransaction a1 and a2, and proposal B of MetaTransaction b1.      If A.a1 executes code that triggers a proposal execution, then the execution order overall can potentially      become [A.a1, B.b1, A.a2].

params.votesAbstain: The number of votes abstaining from the proposal.
params.votesAgainst: The number of votes against the proposal.
params.votesFor: The number of votes for the proposal.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.
